        <abstract>
            <p>Invites BS to visit Down. Advises him to call on Daniel Sharpe. Suggests he see the work of the Ordnance Survey in Wales.</p> 
<p>Offers to lend him Murchison’s <hi rend="italic">The Silurian system</hi> [3 vols. (1839)].</p> 
